---
title: Halloumi Superbowl (v) with Cherry Plum Tomatoes
description: From box to table in just 10-minutes, this recipe is the perfect vegetarian solution to busy evenings (or lunchtimes!). Paired with fresh tomatoes, mint, nutritious brown rice and quinoa, this recipe is as nourishing as it is delicious .
